## Service Information

### Main Service: WISE² Edge Appliance
- **Status**: systemctl status wise2-edge
- **Enable**: systemctl enable wise2-edge
- **Start**: systemctl start wise2-edge
- **Stop**: systemctl stop wise2-edge
- **Logs**: journalctl -u wise2-edge -f

### Health Check Timer
- **Status**: systemctl status wise2-health-check.timer
- **Interval**: Every 30 minutes (configurable)

## API Endpoints

### Status & Health
- `GET /health` - Service health status
- `GET /status` - Detailed runtime status
- `GET /health/metrics` - Performance metrics
- `GET /health/report` - Health report

### Commands
- `POST /commands` - Execute AI commands locally
- `POST /voice/speak` - Text-to-speech

### Hardware Control
- `POST /gpio/:pin` - GPIO pin control
- `POST /camera/capture` - Capture image from camera

### Automation
- `GET /automations/triggers` - List all triggers
- `POST /automations/triggers` - Create new trigger

### Synchronization
- `POST /sync` - Trigger sync with cloud

